body:
Gday guys, I am Blair "Lycanthrope" Trembath I am a streamer and aspiring shout caster. I have been making youtube videos and streaming for about 3 years now however I was formally known as OronarAu. I am not very good at the game but I have been told by viewers I can be very funny and entertaining plus im adorable :) I try to stream at least 7 days a week. my schedule for my stream can be found in the description of the video but I will post it below here as well. I would really appreciate any feedback you can give on the video and the others on my channel as well as if you would check out my social medias follow me there and come check my stream
